            {"type": "list", "title": "A practical shape checklist", "items": ["What does each dimension mean?", "Which dimensions should stay the same after this operation?", "Which dimension am I adding, removing, or collapsing?", "If broadcasting happens, along which axis is the smaller tensor expanding?"]},
